<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8399375">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8399375/" class="title-link">身处历史之中的历史评说</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8399375"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/48051798/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u48051798-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/48051798/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">沈一默</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-03-05"
      class="main-meta">2017-03-05 20:01:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8399375_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  提起中国通史，首先想到便是著名的史学家吕思勉先生，吕先生出生于1884年，那时中国还处在清政府的统治之下，吕先生幼学经史子集，其后专心致力于史学，写下了《中国通史》、《白话本国史》、《史籍与史学》等著作。不过这一版本的《中国通史》却并非仅由吕思勉先生独著，而是...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8399375/#comments">(14回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">35有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8399375_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8399375_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8428193">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8428193/" class="title-link">一部通史三家言</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8428193"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/154957264/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u154957264-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/154957264/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">关山情16</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-03-21"
      class="main-meta">2017-03-21 08:25:28</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8428193_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  <p class="main-title-tip">
                    这篇书评可能有关键情节透露
                  </p>
                  <div class="toggle_review">
